snippet.title: Strato Freaks 2 (Demo 3 / Early Alpha Release)
snippet.description:
ITCH: https://superfreaksdev.itch.io/strato-freaks-2
SFGHQ: https://www.sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/super-freaks-presents-strato-freaks-2.2231/

Here's the Strato Freaks 2 SAGE demo!! All of the Mystic Island and Normal World levels are in, including THAT level (TV Tower). A bunch of new characters are in too; I'm happy to announce that every single character from Strato 1 will be returning (except for probably Earless since it's literally a version of Sonic)!! Please enjoy this small pool of characters for now.
